text: Valentina Marocchi (born 15 December 1983) is an Italian diver. She was born in Bolzano. She finished 23rd in the 3 metre springboard event of the 2004 Olympic Games, 32nd in the 10 metre platform event of the 2004 Olympic Games and fifteenth in the 10 metre platform event of the 2008 Olympic Games. ==References== Category:Italian female divers Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Divers at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Divers at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic divers of Italy Category:Sportspeople from Bolzano Category:Divers of Centro Sportivo Carabinieri
